ntioned property, have decided to sell the said property to the Party of the FIRST PART (PURCHASER).</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">WHEREAS THE SELLER is absolutely seized and possessed Immovable Property R. S. No. 244, T. P. Scheme no. 27 , Final Plot no. 68, admeasuring 2610 sq. mtrs. Non Agricultural Land of mouje : Tandalja Ta: Vadodara in the Registration District and Sub District Vadodara more particularly described in the <strong>Schedule-A </strong>hereinafter written and herein under referred to as said property/said land.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">That the Original owner of the land bearing R. S. No. 244, T. P. Scheme no. 27, Final Plot no.68, admeasuring 2610 sq. mtrs. [out of 4350 sq. mtrs.] Non Agricultural Land of mouje Tandalja Ta: Vadodara i.e. Lalbhai Dadubhai Meer, executed Reg. Sale Deed no. 5636 dtd. 03/04/2019 in favour of Party of the Second Party i.e. M/s Akshar Anmol a partnership firm through its Partner Vipulkumar Jamnadas Dharsandia.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-right:8px; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;\">That the Collector of Vadodara had issue N.A. order vide no. N.A./S.R./2018-19 no. Jamin-D/Kalam-65/Vashi/299 to 307/2018 dtd. 30/01/2019 for R.S.no. 244, having T.P. Scheme no. 27, F.P.no 68, admeasuring 4350 Sq. Mtrs. land of mouje: Tandalja. Ta: Vadodara</span></span></span></p>\n\n